# Wazuh SIEM + XDR Deployment

This file documents the deployment, configuration, network setup, troubleshooting, and agent installation of Wazuh v4.14.5 in the SOC homelab environment.

## Objective

Deploy Wazuh as an all-in-one SIEM and XDR platform to collect, analyze, and correlate security events from all endpoints in the lab, and later integrate with MISP, TheHive, and Cortex.

## Deployment Decision

The Wazuh platform can be deployed as separate components (server, indexer, dashboard on individual VMs) or as a single all-in-one appliance. For this lab, the **Wazuh OVA appliance v4.14.5** was chosen — it bundles the server, indexer, and dashboard into a single VM, which is appropriate for a homelab environment.

